    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776810/extras/1c6bb0b303a933f23aa592240784711f.avif?t=1745486425\" width=600 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you believe in gods? In monsters? In ghosts? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776810/extras/caf935bea1307db65fa8c08df5e942da.poster.avif?t=1745486425\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776810/extras/caf935bea1307db65fa8c08df5e942da.webm?t=1745486425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776810/extras/caf935bea1307db65fa8c08df5e942da.mp4?t=1745486425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>17 years ago, a boy met a monster.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Inn Between is a BL fantasy romance visual novel following Myka Riley and his life long search to recover his missing memories after an accident as a child left him in the care of his aunt with no recollection of who he was, or what happened to his family.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776810/extras/1c0af5dd8dfbb8ae02265512d3a51c75.avif?t=1745486425\" width=600 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One phone call, and his life will change forever. Myka's journey to recover his identity leads him down a unknown and mystical path, revealing a world he never could have imagined existed - a world far removed from the one he knows, filled with gods, ghosts, and creatures only thought myth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776810/extras/efbe2be371f02222940bd89e73a5350b.avif?t=1745486425\" width=600 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can Myka navigate his new reality? As his new relationships bloom, will he succeed in his quest for identity? Or will the forces of an ancient fate claim a long sought victory?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With three romanceable characters, Myka will encounter and grow his connections to those around him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776810/extras/2fc16c182658c9bb2d0e8c48b309961f.avif?t=1745486425\" width=600 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The extended demo follows the common route up to chapter six! </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~50,000 words  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Possible bad ending</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introduces all three romanceable characters </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eight CGs and thirty unique backgrounds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original Soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776810/extras/a7ef192a3334374e632ddb9ae1342365.avif?t=1745486425\" width=600 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gorgeous character after gorgeous character, The Inn Between contains over 20 incredible characters, many of which you can meet in our extended demo! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776810/extras/7907e52182f77a6d36cdf404fb5dd328.avif?t=1745486425\" width=600 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Myka Riley</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mythology nerd with an obsessive love of cats and a deep fear of ghosts. Myka carries a sketch pad full of creatures no one else could see... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776810/extras/66f6daf800d1fd82c18ec6b984fd3956.poster.avif?t=1745486425\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776810/extras/66f6daf800d1fd82c18ec6b984fd3956.webm?t=1745486425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776810/extras/66f6daf800d1fd82c18ec6b984fd3956.mp4?t=1745486425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Follow three separate routes, discover the unique stories of the people Myka meets in his journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Emrys - The Cat God</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leon - The Childhood Friend</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solas - The Fallen God </p>",
